{"tid":244073,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【旺角騷亂】高級警：被告手機藏燒雜物相故拘捕","createTime":"2017-05-15T06:54:21.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-15T09:01:26.000Z","uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"175a114f2998cd8cf59f7da000ebff2a10b1bd16","tid":244073,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T06:54:21.000Z","msg":"大年初二凌晨旺角發生騷亂事件，被控暴動罪的其中5名被告今於區域法院繼續受審。多次形容示威者為滋示份子及暴徒的高級警員李耀雄稱，當日他在彌敦道設立封鎖線，約早上8時見一行5人走近警方防線，李指他相信對方涉及非法集會，故向他們盤查。李於首被告楊子軒的手機內發現有1至2張集會及燒雜物的相，故將他拘捕，惟李在盤問時承認不能確定該些照片的來源。而首被告當時聲稱自己剛用膳完打算乘車離開。<br />\n<br />\n另一高級警員戚健輝出庭作供時，表示同樣留意到該5人表情慌張，又繞過警員而行，認為有可疑於是上前截查。當時次被告羅浩彥稱與另名4人「睇人掟石同放火」，而羅手機內亦藏有人毀壞的士及欄杆的短片，故將次被告拘捕。<br />\n<br />\n5名被告為楊子軒（18歲）、羅浩彥（20歲）、陳紹鈞（48歲）、孫君和（27歲）及連潤發（26歲），他們被控3項暴動罪，指他們在2016年2月9日於旺角豉油街近花園街交界，連同其他人士參與暴動。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170515&amp;guid=56695650&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170515%26guid%3D56695650%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant&d=QSug7dhZHD7voFbR5lwplbIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=0150cd0f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170515%26guid%3D56695650%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant&h=5be88062\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170515&amp;guid=56695650&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant</a><br />\n<br />\n有J圖就係強姦犯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c4ebdbec1c65b47705e1f5b3236e07a2187e26b","tid":244073,"uid":10064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T08:01:43.000Z","msg":"好難見到警察唔行開<br />\n打人前科"},{"pid":"f190c05f28cf277f0add242e35538b883b6619a3","tid":244073,"uid":17646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T08:17:47.000Z","msg":"有偷拍圖就係偷拍<br />\n有其他女自拍相就係偷野"},{"pid":"505710dc7f703f8a552c682322b7a2039948d1e4","tid":244073,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T09:01:26.000Z","msg":"藏有連登app呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}